  "detailed_description": "XOMBEE MPFPS is a Solo Project made using Unreal Engine 4.26 <br />\r\nA FPS played Solo or Online Multiplayer with 3rd Person view added in  <br />\r\nThe Game is Mutant vs Humans with some Maps also containing XOMBEE's to fight as well . 7 Unique Levels to play <br />\r\nMaps included are : Conquest , Rush , Vehicle , Team Death Match , Death Match , Capture the Flag , Kill Confirmed  <br />\r\n4 Character Classes - Assault , Medic , Support , Scout<br />\r\nSome of Weapons included are : Shotgun , Assault Rifle , Sniper Rifle , LMG , 9 mm , Grenades and more ...<br />\r\nSome of the Perks included are - Jet Pack , Med Bot , Speed Boost , Mine and more .....<br />\r\nUp to 32 Players and/or Ai Bots  <br />\r\n8 Different Soldiers on 2 Teams <br />\r\nAlpha Team  includes 1-Robot Girl and 3-Male Tech Soldiers <br />\r\nBeta Team includes 4 - Mutants<br />\r\nWith Regular Updates Planned .........................    Thanks for Playing !!!",
